@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="container">
    <h1 style="margin-top:20px;">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p>At Elegant Furniture, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you visit our website or make a purchase from us.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect various types of information when you interact with our website. This may include:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, shipping address, phone number, and payment details when you make a purchase.</li>
        <li><strong>Non-Personal Information:</strong> Browser type, device information, and browsing patterns through cookies and similar technologies.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>To process and fulfill your orders.</li>
        <li>To improve our website and customer service.</li>
        <li>To send promotional materials and newsletters (you can opt-out at any time).</li>
        <li>To respond to your inquiries or provide customer support.</li>
        <li>To comply with legal requirements.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties, except in the following situations:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>When required by law or to protect our legal rights.</li>
        <li>With trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our website or conducting business (e.g., payment processors, shipping companies).</li>
        <li>In the case of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, your information may be transferred to the new owners.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to enhance your experience on our website. Cookies are small files stored on your device that help us track and target your preferences. You can disable cookies through your browser settings, but this may affect your ability to use some features of our site.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Request access to the personal information we hold about you.</li>
        <li>Request corrections or updates to your personal information.</li>
        <li>Request the deletion of your personal information.</li>
        <li>Opt-out of receiving marketing communications from us.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We take the security of your data seriously and implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect it. However, no method of data transmission or storage is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee its absolute security.</p>

    <h2>Changes to Our Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or applicable laws. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage you to review it periodically.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your information, please contact us at:</p>
    <p>
        Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@elegantfurniture.com">privacy@elegantfurniture.com</a><br />
        Phone: (123) 456-7890
    </p>
</div>
